# Docs Navigator MCP

A powerful documentation assistant that combines **Model Context Protocol (MCP)** with **Claude AI** to provide intelligent Q&A over your documentation files. Built with FastMCP and Gradio for an easy-to-use web interface.

## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ” **Smart Document Search**: Full-text search across your documentation files
- ğŸ¤– **AI-Powered Responses**: Uses Claude AI to provide intelligent answers based on your docs
- ğŸ“ **Multi-Format Support**: Works with `.md`, `.txt`, `.rst`, `.pdf`, and image files
- ğŸ”¤ **OCR Capabilities**: Extract text from image-based PDFs and standalone images using Tesseract OCR
- ğŸ“„ **Advanced PDF Support**: Hybrid PDF processing with automatic fallback to OCR for scanned documents
- ğŸŒ **Web Interface**: Clean Gradio-based chat interface
- âš¡ **MCP Integration**: Leverages Model Context Protocol for seamless tool integration
- ğŸ”§ **Easy Setup**: Simple configuration and deployment

